<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Delivery Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      Congratulations! Your item, {{itemname}}, has been successfully delivered. The amount of<strong>{{itemprice}} </strong> along with the delivery fee has been credited to your account. You may now request a withdrawal of these funds at your convenience.
    </p>
    <p>
      Note:Charges applied will be romoved upon withdrawal.
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for using Thriftify. To upload and sell more of your items, click the link below:
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{link}}">Sell More Items</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      Kind regards,<br />
      The Thriftiffy Team
    </p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
